The Block Australia Fans vs Faves Series 8 Episode 29

The Block is back with a Fans versus Favorites format - will the old hands prevail?

Kitchen week is always stressful and one couple starts without a builder. Even our experienced renovators start to crack under the pressure. There's a chance for everyone to cool off with a pool party in the communal area.
